        "opcion_a": "The book is in the table.",
        "opcion_b": "The book is on the table.",
        "correcta": "b"
      },
      "definicion_pragmatica": "We use prepositions of place (in, on, under, next to, behind, in front of, between) to say where something is.",
      "tabla": {
        "titulo": "Where is it?",
        "encabezados": [
          "Preposition",
          "Meaning",
          "Example"
        ],
        "filas": [
